      <title>The Secret Sauce fo Quality Software</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/talks/extreme-programming-the-secret-sauce/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 15:00:26 -0900</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/talks/extreme-programming-the-secret-sauce/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;extreme-programming---𝗧𝗵𝗲-𝗦𝗲𝗰𝗿𝗲𝘁-𝗦𝗮𝘂𝗰𝗲-𝗳𝗼𝗿-𝗛𝗶𝗴𝗵-𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗲𝗱-𝗤𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆-𝗦𝗼𝗳𝘁𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗲&#34; class=&#34;heading&#34;&gt;Extreme Programming - 𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗦𝗲𝗰𝗿𝗲𝘁 𝗦𝗮𝘂𝗰𝗲 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗛𝗶𝗴𝗵-𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗲𝗱, 𝗤𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆 𝗦𝗼𝗳𝘁𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗲&lt;a href=&#34;#extreme-programming---%f0%9d%97%a7%f0%9d%97%b5%f0%9d%97%b2-%f0%9d%97%a6%f0%9d%97%b2%f0%9d%97%b0%f0%9d%97%bf%f0%9d%97%b2%f0%9d%98%81-%f0%9d%97%a6%f0%9d%97%ae%f0%9d%98%82%f0%9d%97%b0%f0%9d%97%b2-%f0%9d%97%b3%f0%9d%97%bc%f0%9d%97%bf-%f0%9d%97%9b%f0%9d%97%b6%f0%9d%97%b4%f0%9d%97%b5-%f0%9d%98%80%f0%9d%97%bd%f0%9d%97%b2%f0%9d%97%b2%f0%9d%97%b1-%f0%9d%97%a4%f0%9d%98%82%f0%9d%97%ae%f0%9d%97%b9%f0%9d%97%b6%f0%9d%98%81%f0%9d%98%86-%f0%9d%97%a6%f0%9d%97%bc%f0%9d%97%b3%f0%9d%98%81%f0%9d%98%84%f0%9d%97%ae%f0%9d%97%bf%f0%9d%97%b2&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;extreme-programming---𝗧𝗵𝗲-𝗦𝗲𝗰𝗿𝗲𝘁-𝗦𝗮𝘂𝗰𝗲-𝗳𝗼𝗿-𝗛𝗶𝗴𝗵-𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗲𝗱-𝗤𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆-𝗦𝗼𝗳𝘁𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗲&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 640 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Join us as we delve into the intriguing world of Extreme Programming (XP), a methodology that has revolutionized the pace and quality of software development. We&amp;rsquo;ll dissect the practices that constitute XP and explore why they are instrumental in more rapidly delivering superior software.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
