    <item>
      <title>Team Programming - Conference Workshop</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/talks/team-programming-at-conferences/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Apr 2023 15:00:26 -0900</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/talks/team-programming-at-conferences/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;team-programming---conference-workshop&#34; class=&#34;heading&#34;&gt;Team Programming - Conference Workshop&lt;a href=&#34;#team-programming---conference-workshop&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;team-programming---conference-workshop&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 640 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Whole Team Programming, also known as &lt;em&gt;Mobbing&lt;/em&gt;, or &lt;em&gt;Ensemble Programming&lt;/em&gt;, is a practice of whole-team collaboration&#xA;that&#xA;produces higher quality, more rapidly delivered code than solo development.&#xA;Participants will learn the basics of communicating as a group, how a team can select and break down work, and why this&#xA;practice far outpaces a team of Individual Contributors.&#xA;We will collaborate as a group to write code and learn how to work effectively with multiple team members with varying&#xA;levels of experience.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Working The Way We Want</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/talks/working-the-way-we-want/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Apr 2023 15:00:26 -0900</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/talks/working-the-way-we-want/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;working-the-way-we-want&#34; class=&#34;heading&#34;&gt;Working the Way We Want&lt;a href=&#34;#working-the-way-we-want&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;working-the-way-we-want&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 640 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Starting in 2016, I was part of an amazing experiment of 40+ people who self-organized and dynamically re-teamed around&#xA;our work, using two-day iterations to produce amazing high-quality applications for a large healthcare insurance&#xA;company.&#xA;Our process became what is now called Fluid Scaling Technology (&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.fastagile.io/home&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer nofollow&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FAST&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-up-right-from-square fa-2xs&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-up-right-from-square fa-2xs&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 512 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-up-right-from-square&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
